"your-questions-answered/): **Citizens’ Assemblies: Your Questions Answered**"
"\\ XR UK’s Citizens’ Assembly Working Group explain what exactly the 3rd "
"Demand means and answer detailed questions that rebels have been asking "
"about citizens’ assemblies."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: 2021-02-09-global-newsletter-48.md:313
